# SSH Banner for Aether Mailer
# Displayed on successful SSH connection

================================================================================
                      AETHER MAILER - SECURE ACCESS POINT
================================================================================

Welcome to Aether Mailer CLI interface!

You are accessing a production mail server system.
All connections are logged and monitored.

IMPORTANT:
- This system is for authorized users only
- All activities are recorded for security purposes
- Unauthorized access attempts will be reported

Type 'mailer help' to see available commands
Type 'exit' to disconnect

================================================================================